$$A\times x = b \pmod p$$
$A$
$$ \left[
\begin{array}{ccc}
  a_0&a_1&a_2&a_3\\\\
  a_1&a_0&a_3&a_2\\\\
  a_2&a_3&a_0&a_1\\\\
